column13:
Here's the following Timeline based on print type from approval date:

• Digital print: 3-5 working days
• Metallic print: 3-5 working days
• Foil print* matte stock, premium stock, 270gsm color stock and vellum stock: 7-10 working days

column10:
To answer your first question "How long does it take to receive an order.
I have saved engagement invites, quantity of 40. Just curious what your turn around time is to make sure the timing is right."

So once you put through your order it takes us up to 48 hours to come back with the first design proof. 
Here are the following Timeline based on print type from approval date:

• Digital print: 3-5 working days
• Metallic print: 3-5 working days
• Foil print: 7-10 working days
• Letterpress: 10-12 working days
• Letterpress + Foil: 10-12 working days
• Print on wood: 5-7 working days
• Magnets: 5-7 working days
• Raised Foil: 10 working days
column13: As for the coupon codes, unfortunately we don't have first time customer vouchers, the only discount we have right now is if you purchase more than three types of cards, you will get 15% off the whole order
